  "text": "A comprehensive search of the apache/kafka (sg-evals/kafka--0753c489) and apache/flink (sg-evals/flink--0cc95fcc) repositories was conducted to find references to three deprecated Kafka producer configuration keys: 'block.on.buffer.full', 'metadata.fetch.timeout.ms', and 'timeout.ms' (the old producer timeout, replaced by 'delivery.timeout.ms'). The search included Java source files, test files, and configuration documentation files across both repositories. No references to any of these three deprecated producer configuration keys were found in either repository. This indicates that either these configurations have already been removed from the current versions of these codebases, or they were never utilized in these specific versions of Apache Kafka and Apache Flink."
}

